using Microsoft.Extensions.AI.OpenAI;
using OpenAI.Chat;

// Create OpenAI ChatClient (from OpenAI SDK)
var openAIChatClient = new ChatClient("gpt-4o", apiKey: "your-key");

// Wrap it as an IChatClient
IChatClient chatClient = new OpenAIChatClient(openAIChatClient);
```

**Key classes:**
- `OpenAIChatClient` (namespace: `Microsoft.Extensions.AI.OpenAI`)
- Constructor: `OpenAIChatClient(OpenAI.Chat.ChatClient)`

